771
01:16:30.157 --> 01:16:31.225
Okay.

772
01:16:32.561 --> 01:16:35.463
And. by the way.
clean your neck. please.

773
01:16:35.530 --> 01:16:37.331
Okay.

774
01:16:38.899 --> 01:16:41.035
