775
01:16:41.102 --> 01:16:44.338
She's starting
to fucking lose it.

776
01:17:03.190 --> 01:17:04.692
Holy shit.

777
01:17:06.528 --> 01:17:10.898
You know what?
I don't think anyone is
going to recognize you.

778
01:17:10.965 --> 01:17:12.433
You did.

779
01:17:12.500 --> 01:17:15.402
Yeah. 'cause I was there. I
