in the video.

781
01:17:32.353 --> 01:17:36.290
So was it like kind of
self-defense or kind of?

782
01:17:38.292 --> 01:17:39.393
No.

783
01:17:44.431 --> 01:17:45.900
<i>No?</i>

784
01:17:48.035 --> 01:17:49.203
No.

785
01:17:51.506 --> 01:17:53.741
Okay. What do you want me to do?

786
01:17:53.807 --> 01:17:55.843
I don't know.
It's your ticket. not mine.

787
01:17:55.910 --> 01:17:58.078
It doesn't break
any of our rules.

788
01:17:58.145 --> 01:18:00.214
so deleting it might bring
more attention.

789
01:18:00.281 --> 01:18:02.116
I don't want to get you
into any trouble.

790
01:18:05.286 --> 01:18:07.556
Maybe I deserve
to be in trouble.

791
01:18:07.622 --> 01:18:08.989
Daisy. it's not you.

792
01:18:09.056 --> 01:18:12.092
It's this fucking place.
it's not you.

793
01:18:13.427 --> 01:18:16.463
It's got a lot of views. The
guy never filed a police report.

794
01:18:16.531 --> 01:18:21.068
I checked. so you're probably
