840
01:22:09.798 --> 01:22:12.700
because it feels like our
fates are intertwined.

841
01:22:12.767 --> 01:22:17.438
and I can't feel free until I
fucking do something about it.

842
01:22:18.272 --> 01:22:20.675
But that's simply not true.
Daisy.

843
01:22:20.742 --> 01:22:22.376
How do you know that?

844
01:22:22.443 --> 01:22:28.015
Because if it were true. you'd
be talking to him now. not me.

845
01:22:36.190 --> 01:22:38.626
Just a sec. wait. What?

846
01:22:38.693 --> 01:22:40.795
I quit.

847
01:22:40.862 --> 01:22:43.665
Your employee contract
requires two weeks' notice

848
01:22:43.731 --> 01:22:45.466
before resignation takes effect.

849
01:22:45.533 --> 01:22:47.902
If you don't oblige.
we'll take it to court.

850
01:22:48.035 --> 01:22:49.737
Two weeks it is.

851
01:23:31.713 --> 01:23:33.080
No!

852
01:23:33.080 --> 01:23:35.382
Fuck! No!

853
01:23:35.449 --> 01:23:36.818
Fuck! Aah!

854
01:23:36.885 --> 01:23:38.653
Poor guy.

855
01:23:39.654 --> 01:23:40.722
Fuck!

856
01:25:46.213 --> 01:25:48.315
Don't fucking do it. bro.

857
01:26:18.445 --> 01:26:19.747
Okay. I get it.

858
01:26:52.146 --> 01:26:53.748
Daisy Morris?

859
01:26:59.721 --> 01:27:02.289
Tell me something
you learned at your last job.

860
01:27:02.355 --> 01:27:07.394
Well. I was in tech.
and while I learned
nothing about computers.

861
01:27:07.461 --> 01:27:09.163
it taught me a lot about people.

862
01:27:09.296 --> 01:27:13.067
Because that's what the
internet is. It's just people.

863
01:27:13.134 --> 01:27:16.537
And for a while my biggest
desire was to help these people.

864
01:27:16.604 --> 01:27:18.673
which is why I wanted
to be a nurse.

865
01:27:18.740 --> 01:27:22.409
Yes. that's why many
young men and women
enter the field of medicine.

866
01:27:22.476 --> 01:27:24.377
I'm sure you hear this
all the time. but...

867
01:27:24.444 --> 01:27:30.551
we think we need to devote
ourselves to something
noble and altruistic.

868
01:27:30.618 --> 01:27:34.989
Something that makes our lives
meaningful and important.

869
01:27:35.056 --> 01:27:39.560
but this job taught me that
not everyone deserves...

870
01:27:39.627 --> 01:27:40.828
